      "content": "That's a bit of a relief to hear, but I'm seeing some conflicting reports. Several satellite imagery analysts have flagged significant movement in the heavy artillery divisions near the DMZ, not just 'symbolic' troop shifts. Even some of our field assets are reporting increased radio silence and unusual logistical surges in those sectors. Are you saying those specific movements aren't being factored into your assessment of the escalation risk?",
